---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Services
description: MOT, servicing, diagnostics and repairs at Nandrews Garage Ltd.
bodyClass: page-standard page-services
---
<section class="page-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="services-banner">
      <img src="/assets/images/nandrews-location.webp" alt="Nandrews Garage location">
      <div class="services-banner-title">
        <h1 class="page-title">Our Services</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-block services-detail-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="services-detail-shell">
      <div class="services-detail-list">
        {% for service in services %}
        <article class="service-detail-row">
          <div class="service-card service-detail-card">
            <img src="{{ service.image }}" alt="{{ service.title }}">
          </div>
          <div class="service-detail-copy">
            <h2>{{ service.title }}</h2>
            {% for paragraph in service.details %}
            <p>{{ paragraph }}</p>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-panel services-cta-panel">
      <div>
        <span class="section-kicker">Not sure what you need?</span>
        <h2>Call the garage and explain what the vehicle is doing.</h2>
        <p>If the issue is not obvious, that is exactly what diagnostics are for. The goal is to point people in the right direction quickly, not make them guess which service label fits best.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-brand btn-lg" href="/contact/">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
